          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUGPeK2NsvoM8D3eddyuPsPDTeg0JrhwahXshfVvHXrSqqs6Gqo=s120-c-rp-mo-br100",
          "description": "Incredibly disorganized. They call you every day to make an appointment and keep calling every day even after you\u2019ve made one. Front desk is incredibly rude and no one has any clue what is going on. After hounding me for weeks about an appointment I\u2019d already made, when I showed up they told me they couldn\u2019t see me because the doctor on my insurance card didn\u2019t match their doctor\u2014despite the fact that I\u2019ve been seen here already multiple times. Don\u2019t waste your time with these people.",
