          "user_review_count": 4,
          "user_photo_count": 9,
          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK7G9z40zGRoQp2JZYEzpbqXmP2BlYk4Xzd9h09gwHtNtfMrQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100",
          "description": "I\u2019ve been coming here for several years, the front desk is always on point and makes sure to accommodate you as best they can.\n\nDoctor Yana is wonderful, she listens, is very thorough and doesn\u2019t leave anything behind. She explains everything in a way everyone can understand. She also finds solutions with you for you to have different outlets to get better.\n\nThe practice is super well located and takes most insurance. There\u2019s a great coffee shop nearby if you have a little wait too :)",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURzNE9pbVFBEAE!2m1!1s0x0:0x44f1d70f5d5d181!3m1!1s2@1:CIHM0ogKEICAgIDs4OimQA%7C%7C?hl=en",
