          "description": "I think you really want to avoid here if your condition is more serious because it could be dangerous. The place was a bit better when it was at old location. This is affordable and quick check up clinic but admin is an absolute mess to the point you can't even make an appointment and/or they assign you without even asking and miss the appointments without your knowledge. And there's NO WAY you can communicate with them.\nBut most concerning is their sloppiness for the medication. They don't refill your meds and not even answering calls which potentially lead your health to a risk.",
