          "description": "Me and my husband have been a patient at Lenox Medical for the past 3yrs. We both saw Yana as she's our primary physician. She's amazing and to the point. We have also seen the cardiologist Dr. Sanghi for regular precautionary check ups and he is very good too. So far we are really very pleased with the clinic and their services. All the staff are very kind and helpful and it's a very clean establishment.",
